Usage
After starting the application, you can access it by navigating to http://localhost:8080 in your browser. Here are some example API routes:

GET /opportunities - Lists all opportunities
POST /opportunities - Creates a new opportunity
GET /opportunities/{id} - Retrieves a specific opportunity by ID
PUT /opportunities/{id} - Updates an existing opportunity
DELETE /opportunities/{id} - Deletes an opportunity
